title: Formula 1 2015 United States Qualifying Rain Dance 720p HD
description:
Formula 1 2015 United States Qualifying Rain Dance 720p HD
Video : TS; MPEG; 1280x720; 16:9; 25 fps; ~2000 kbps
Audio : English (AAC; 48 KHz; 2 ch; 128 kbps)
Duration: 3hr 5mins

Note: This 3 hours includes rain dancing, interviews, Analysis and waiting for the rain to stop with updates every half hour if the session is going to take place or not. Finally, it was decided that Qualifying will take place on Sunday morning after heavy rain in Austin prevented the session going ahead as scheduled
